name: Roger Henri
description: I want to spend my time loving this person and missing when them when they are not there and can’t wait to get to them. I want to walk hand in hand and leave love notes for them everywhere. Love is a noble act of self-giving, offering trust, faith, and loyalty. The more you love, the more you lose a part of yourself, yet you don’t become less of who you are; you end up being complete with your loved ones. I love to touch and be touched. I also love the outdoors, sports and boating..
